pageContext.claim: “The son who didn't have a job, who got thrown out of the Navy, who was really down and out, all of a sudden is making millions and millions and millions of dollars.”
pageContext.analysis: At various times, Trump has charged that Hunter Biden unemployed for years or did not have a job until his father became vice president. That's false. He used his political connections to continuously have a variety of jobs in Washington in government, lobbying and consulting.
